4. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possibility as the paper may involve analyzing the complexity of the algorithm used to derive the new bound. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper mentions the Ulam's liar game and its relation to channel coding.
